    { "text": "because who reads the back of a Febreze can?", "fromSec": 38.8, "toSec": 41.1 },
    { "text": "and number three is my favorite, for the *audacity*", "fromSec": 41.1, "toSec": 45.266 },
    { "text": "*Dawn Platinum* — the bottle now says, and I'm quoting", "fromSec": 45.7, "toSec": 49.5 },
